name: Taupō
description: Key lime, spanish cedar, and freshly zested orange. Medium straw hue, meringue-like foam.   Riwaka, Wakatu, Citra

name: Tides
description: Citrus, passionfruit and cantaloupe. Blueberry aroma. El Dorado, Citra, Mosaic, Simcoe

name: Drip
description: White grape, grapefruit and orange.  Phantasm, Motueka, Nelson Sauvin, Citra

name: Hanno
description: Resinous, dank, notes of douglas fir with citrus and lychee. Mosaic, Comet, Triumph, and USDA Elite Line 008

name: Rubico
description: Pineapple, peach rings, bubblegum, strawberry and citrus.  Estate Grown Comet, Vic Secret, Galaxy

name: Elias
description: Smooth, subtle citrus notes and floral aroma.

name: Grandar
description: Bready, floral and herbal notes with a citrus finish. Step mashed and hopped with Hallertauer Mittelfrüh and Saaz.

name: Levenator
description: Rich malt flavor with notes of toasted caramel, dark fruit, and chocolate.

name: Terra
description: Orange zest, marmalade, and grapefruit. Floral and spicy.   Wakatu, Motueka
